<Weakness xmlns="http://cwe.mitre.org/cwe-7" xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" ID="352" Name="Cross-Site Request Forgery (CSRF)" Abstraction="Compound" Structure="Composite" Status="Stable" Diagram="/data/images/CWE-352-Diagram.png">
         <Description>The web application does not, or cannot, sufficiently verify whether a request was intentionally provided by the user who sent the request, which could have originated from an unauthorized actor. </Description>
